Between 100 and 110 min of the simulation, GPS spoofing error of 100 m is added. In order to simulate the process that a smart attacker deceives the GPS receiver from a slow speed, a gradually increasing GPS error with a growth rate ranging from 0.01 m/s to 6 m/s is added from 150 to 240 min.
